47
00:02:50,639 --> 00:02:51,520
The truth is,

48
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:55,880
I came from another Dongyue.

49
00:02:56,679 --> 00:02:57,839
Over there,

50
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,559
