51
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:05,279
Tan Er was another person, not me.

52
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,240
She had passed away.

53
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:10,160
It's only me now.

54
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,559
Is that true?

55
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:46,440
So this was why you seemed like
a different person after you fell ill.

56
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,399
You even started to treat me differently.

57
00:03:48,399 --> 00:03:49,880
You became much friendlier.

58
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,720
So this was the reason.

59
00:03:53,359 --> 00:03:56,679
What about the original Eighth Brother?

60
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,160
The original Eighth Brother...

61
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,559
