65
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,600
Without you,

66
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:22,959
I would have lost my Eighth Brother

67
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:25,440
and never know the joy you brought me.

68
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,760
I had this feeling long ago

69
00:04:34,559 --> 00:04:37,040
that you were different from before.

70
00:04:37,559 --> 00:04:38,959
I had my guesses.

71
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:41,720
But I couldn't believe it.

72
00:04:50,239 --> 00:04:51,119
If...

73
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:54,760
both you and Princess were here,
that would be great.

74
00:04:57,239 --> 00:04:59,519
I could protect both of you.

75
00:05:03,239 --> 00:05:04,040
Jing Xin.

76
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,480
Sorry.

77
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:10,320
I should have told you long ago.

78
00:05:13,559 --> 00:05:16,239
I know you and Tan Er shared a deep bond.

79
00:05:16,839 --> 00:05:19,600
I know you wouldn't be mad at me.

80
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,600
But I still feel sorry about it.

81
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,640
You may not believe it,

82
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:35,000
I actually met Qu Tan Er in the past.

83
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,440
She was a nice person.

84
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:39,079
We were good friends.

85
00:05:42,239 --> 00:05:43,519
She even saved my life.

86
00:05:51,119 --> 00:05:51,880
All right.

87
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,320
Don't be too upset.

88
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,239
In my heart,

89
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:59,880
you are just as important as the original Princess.

90
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:02,600
I will always be with you and protect you.

91
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,679
All right.

92
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,959
All right.

93
00:06:19,559 --> 00:06:20,679
Don't cry.

94
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,959
Don't forget,

95
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,760
you are a cold-hearted guard.

96
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,239
All right.

97
00:06:31,359 --> 00:06:32,799
Why is everyone crying?

98
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,440
I don't really understand

99
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,760
all the stories you told us.

100
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,880
But one thing is certain.

101
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:40,880
You are all good people.

102
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,760
You are all my friends.

103
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:44,239
That's all that matters.

104
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:45,760
He's right.

105
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:49,160
The whole story was baffling,

106
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:51,200
but you have my gratitude nonetheless

107
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,040
for being honest with us.

108
00:06:54,679 --> 00:06:58,440
We will return to our world someday,

109
00:06:59,679 --> 00:07:03,880
but I'm grateful that we met.

110
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,079
Since we will part ways sooner or later,

111
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,040
why not drink to our hearts' content?

112
00:07:09,679 --> 00:07:10,480
Cheers.

113
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:11,480
Cheers.

114
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,160
Cheers!

115
00:08:23,559 --> 00:08:25,679
