121
00:08:41,719 --> 00:08:44,200
We both know why you are here.

122
00:08:45,640 --> 00:08:46,799
Send this message to Her Majesty.

123
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:49,880
I will fulfill my end of the promise.

124
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:56,159
I will protect what is precious to me.

125
00:08:58,119 --> 00:08:59,359
Are you going to let me go?

126
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,559
This might be your only chance

127
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:06,239
to get rid of me for good in a righteous way.

128
00:09:09,119 --> 00:09:10,080
You saved her life once.

129
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,159
You have an honorable heart.

130
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,719
I've never thought about taking your life.

131
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:36,000
He was Mo Yi Feng's right-hand man.

132
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:40,559
His skills in strategies and martial arts
are undoubtedly outstanding.

133
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,960
I got careless.

134
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:47,640
But there is a matter

135
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:49,359
that might be beneficial to Your Majesty.

136
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:50,799
