144
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:08,159
showed up in the border garrison.

145
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:11,119
They all had their names changed.

146
00:10:11,599 --> 00:10:12,599
Mo Yuan Long...

147
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:20,840
Mo Feng Yang shall be stationed
at the border indefinitely.

148
00:10:22,479 --> 00:10:23,200
Yes.

149
00:10:26,208 --> 00:10:29,475
<i>Mo Residence</i>

150
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,000
Father.

151
00:10:44,119 --> 00:10:44,919
Feng Yang.

152
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,799
The yin imperial token has been retrieved.

153
00:10:49,640 --> 00:10:51,640
You will soon be stationed at the border.

154
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:57,440
