156
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,840
I must discuss with you our plan

157
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,719
to get the imperial token back.

158
00:11:01,719 --> 00:11:03,400
Father, why are you doing this?

159
00:11:04,919 --> 00:11:06,919
Defending the border is my duty.

160
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,919
I'm willing to join the campaign.

161
00:11:11,599 --> 00:11:12,880
Do you think you've got this far

162
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,520
on your own capability?

163
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,960
When our Mo family needs you the most,

164
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,520
you have no right to turn us down!

165
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:20,520
What is Mo family you speak of?

166
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,440
Is it the Mo family that needs me?

167
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:24,159
Or is it you that wants my help?

168
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:26,000
It's the Mo family!

169
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,119
Feng Yang.

170
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:31,159
You are the only daughter of our Mo family.

171
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:34,640
Your future is also the future of the Mo family.

172
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,039
My future is at the frontier,

173
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:39,039
on the battlefield, and on my steed.

174
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:43,159
My future will not be part of your scheme.

175
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:52,359
So you know everything.

176
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:56,919
I couldn't believe what you've done.

177
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,000
I didn't want to believe it either.

178
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:02,039
That's because in my heart,

179
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:06,640
you are still the man who teaches me virtues

180
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:09,840
and value of bravery.

181
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:13,799
Indeed, Feng Yang.

182
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:17,799
I put all my hope in you.

183
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,559
I value your strength the most.

184
00:12:19,679 --> 00:12:20,880
Do not become the one

185
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:22,719
who disappoints me the most.

186
00:12:24,119 --> 00:12:26,080
Do you not care

187
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,919
about your children's happiness?

188
00:12:28,119 --> 00:12:30,599
Eldest Brother, Eighth Brother,

189
00:12:30,599 --> 00:12:31,799
and I share the same fate.

190
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,880
Fourteenth has a kind heart,

191
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,679
yet you think nothing of him.

192
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,719
You've even shown him more berating than love.

193
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:40,119
Everyone has let you down.

194
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:42,320
But you have disappointed us too!

195
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,840
Stop it!

196
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:44,880
You...

197
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,400
Have you forgotten

198
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:49,960
your mother's last wish for caring all the people?

199
00:12:50,239 --> 00:12:51,719
I have never forgotten it.

200
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,039
I will never forget it.

201
00:12:59,119 --> 00:12:59,960
Father.

202
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,599
Take care.

203
00:13:09,359 --> 00:13:10,039
You...

204
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:28,919
Her Majesty demoted me
to the rank of commandant.

205
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:31,719
I will set out on a campaign three days from now on.

206
00:13:33,840 --> 00:13:36,280
I will follow you to the edge of the world.

207
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,799
We might never come home.

208
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:38,760
I don't care.

209
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,159
Are you upset that I made the decision

210
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,479
to bring you into war again?

211
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:47,760
I was already tired of this boring place.

212
00:13:48,679 --> 00:13:51,440
The frontier may be a harsh land,
but at least we'll be free there.

213
00:13:57,479 --> 00:13:58,400
Not to mention...

214
00:13:59,599 --> 00:14:01,840
I had longed to fight by your side.

215
00:14:33,159 --> 00:14:34,479
Jing Xuan, behave.

216
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:36,159
Don't make our father mad.

217
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:38,400
You must stop fooling around.

218
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:41,039
Otherwise, Jing Xin might
choose another man over you.

219
00:14:42,159 --> 00:14:43,080
Don't worry.

220
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:45,239
I will keep Fourteenth Young Master safe.

221
00:14:46,119 --> 00:14:47,080
All right.

222
00:14:47,599 --> 00:14:49,760
Is this a confession or a farewell?

223
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,679
Feng Yang, I know you're a fearsome warrior.

224
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,000
But the blades can cut anyone.

225
00:14:56,119 --> 00:14:58,000
You must be careful while you're there.

226
00:14:58,239 --> 00:15:01,239
After all, you have someone to look after.

227
00:15:04,359 --> 00:15:05,919
Don't worry.

228
00:15:05,919 --> 00:15:07,880
I will never let my man live in fear.

229
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:10,440
Look at yourself.

230
00:15:10,799 --> 00:15:12,479
You are acting tough again.

231
00:15:13,359 --> 00:15:15,440
How is it wrong to let him live with ease of mind?

232
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:18,840
Not at all. Love me with all you can.

233
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:21,239
What matters is for us to stay happy.

234
00:15:21,479 --> 00:15:22,960
Ignore what she said.

235
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,159
Ungrateful.

236
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:26,919
I shouldn't have given you
the repudiation paper.

237
00:15:27,159 --> 00:15:30,080
I should have made you suffer
a life of loneliness in your room.

238
00:15:32,559 --> 00:15:34,719
All right, it's time to leave.

239
00:15:35,039 --> 00:15:36,640
It's been two hours since
the main force's departure.

240
00:15:37,119 --> 00:15:39,080
We must reach the outpost before nightfall.

241
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:45,544
♪Every time I yearn for your voices♪

242
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:48,239
Eighth Brother, I must be on my way.

243
00:15:50,359 --> 00:15:51,239
Wait.

244
00:15:53,599 --> 00:15:59,679
♪I slowly move away as I say my goodbye♪

245
00:15:59,679 --> 00:16:00,400
Sorry.

246
00:16:01,479 --> 00:16:04,479
It's my fault for dragging you into this.

247
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:08,799
It's not your fault. We should thank you instead.

248
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:10,239
If it hadn't been for you,

249
00:16:10,479 --> 00:16:13,320
Yun Xiu and I wouldn't have the chance
to live a free life at the frontier.

250
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:15,320
We wouldn't be able to defend our country

251
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:16,440
without distractions.

252
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:19,832
♪Do you understand♪

253
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:23,000
Sister, take care.

254
00:16:25,679 --> 00:16:26,799
Yes, Brother.

255
00:16:30,079 --> 00:16:30,839
Sister.

256
00:16:30,839 --> 00:16:33,655
♪Life was so wonderful♪

257
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:34,479
What is this?

258
00:16:34,719 --> 00:16:37,239
Eldest Brother prepared some
medicine for injuries for you.

259
00:16:39,560 --> 00:16:40,719
Send him my thanks.

260
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,839
Very well, we should go now.

261
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:47,680
Take care.

262
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:48,560
Take care.

263
00:16:49,359 --> 00:16:50,599
- Take care.
- Take care.

264
00:16:51,479 --> 00:16:52,319
Take care.

265
00:16:52,920 --> 00:16:55,839
Prince Consort, shouldn't you join them?

266
00:16:56,520 --> 00:16:58,079
General has been the closest
with you since childhood.

267
00:16:58,680 --> 00:16:59,640
After she's left,

268
00:17:00,119 --> 00:17:01,719
there is no telling if you would meet again.

269
00:17:03,239 --> 00:17:04,040
Never mind.

270
00:17:06,119 --> 00:17:07,199
In her heart,

271
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:10,359
I'm still the Eldest Brother she respects.

272
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:12,239
Isn't that good enough?

273
00:17:14,359 --> 00:17:16,520
I only hope that she follows her heart...

274
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:21,199
