387
00:24:41,079 --> 00:24:42,040
Not to mention...

388
00:24:44,160 --> 00:24:45,880
I shouldn't disrespect Her Highness.

389
00:24:46,040 --> 00:24:47,400
I deserve punishment.

390
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:51,239
Never mind. Carry on.

391
00:24:53,760 --> 00:24:56,280
