394
00:25:02,520 --> 00:25:03,839
Is that true?

395
00:25:04,719 --> 00:25:06,040
I would never lie to Your Majesty.

396
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:12,160
This is certainly weird.

397
00:25:12,839 --> 00:25:14,680
